{"type":"message","id":"7e8b55ce","parentId":"9ec79bd9","timestamp":"2026-07-06T11:33:40.490Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ade13a3e5c7a48579dac728a","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a **photo** of a workspace setup, taken from a low angle with a shallow depth of field. \n\nHere is what the image shows:\n\n*   **Foreground:** A close-up of a thick notebook or planner with a textured, metallic gold (or olive-gold) faux-leather cover. The cover has stitched edges and a closure flap. On the flap, there is an embossed logo that reads **\"BOGUSH\"** inside a square, with some stylized script underneath.\n*   **Mid-ground:** An open laptop (resembling a MacBook) sitting on a light-colored wooden desk. The laptop screen is on but is highly reflective, showing clouds and the sky, making any text on the screen illegible.\n*   **Background:** A window looking out onto green trees and a blue sky with white clouds. To the left, a single red rose is visible on the windowsill, slightly out of focus. \n\nThe image captures a bright, comfortable, and organized work-from-home or study environment."}],"details":{"model":"litellm/gemini/gemini-3.5-flash","image":"media://inbound/ba47f96f-82d2-4dec-98a2-65ab9fdb148f.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783337620488}}
